<plot>Short-lived (3 weeks) summer show about Ernest Harris, a 14-year-old kid whose father only paid attention to the eldest boy, a 16-year-old basketball prodigy named Chester. The boys had a sister named DeeDee. To compensate for his family's lack of interest, Ernest talked to his camcorder about his dreams and ambitions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?530197</url></doc>
